PrecisAcceptance of a REVOCATION OF SURRENDER assented to by the KITSELAS BAND whereby the reserves it surrendered in 1947 for the sale of their timber will be returned to reserve status, to wit, Kitselas Indian Reserve No. 1, Chimdimash Indian Reserves Nos. 2 and 2A, and Kshish Indian Reserve No. 4, all in the Province of British Columbia.
